descp2: (Optional.) A list of `len(datasets)` floating-point values where`weights[i]` represents the probability with which an element should be sampled from `datasets[i]`, or a `tf.data.Dataset` object where each element is such a list. Defaults to a uniform distribution across`datasets`.
